data.description: Welcome to Brittany Place! Open the front door into the open concept living and kitchen space with soaring ceilings. Moving down the hall, you will find 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, the laundry closet and storage closet. The primary bedroom and bathroom are attached, offering comfort and convenience. Step through the French doors onto the back deck overlooking the fenced-in spacious backyard. The backyard also features a storage building and a swing set. This home is located just minutes away from Pinson High School, shopping, and restaurants. The back porch stairs and handrails have been replaced as well the crawl space door.  Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this house your home - it offers location, space, and an attractive price.
